OL,7,F"And whilst the rawness of the wounds
OL,8,Fof the families and regiments who
OL,9,Fsuffered almost unimaginable loss that
OL,10,Fnight may have dulled a little over
OL,11,Fthe years, the depth of their loss is
OL,12,Fincalculable.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
