OL,7,F"And then, of course, there's the
OL,8,Fpolicing and the judicial mess as
OL,9,Fwell, which has lived on for decades
OL,10,Fafter the physical mess in the town
OL,11,Fcentre was cleared up: the arrest of
OL,12,Fthe so-called Guildford Four for the
OL,13,Fbombings themselves and the Maguire
OL,14,FSeven for allegedly aiding and
OL,15,Fabetting them.
OL,17,F"The mess of unsafe convictions based
OL,18,Fon partial evidence and confessions
OL,19,Fobtained by coercion, the continuing
OL,20,Fmess of crimes unsolved and
OL,21,Fperpetrators unpunished.
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU
