OL,7,F"We may understand the huge pressures
OL,8,Funder which the Metropolitan Police
OL,9,Fwere operating at the height of the
OL,10,FTroubles.
OL,12,F"We may recognise too the complexities
OL,13,Fof that continuing quest for justice
OL,14,Fafter half a century has come and gone.
