OL,5,Cbombings
OL,7,F"We may be thankful for the Good
OL,8,FFriday Agreement, and that the
OL,9,Findiscriminate bombing of our towns
OL,10,Fand cities by Irish paramilitaries has
OL,11,Flong ceased, but crimes unsolved and
OL,12,Fperpetrators unpunished still leave so
OL,13,Fmuch up in the air, with closure hard
OL,14,Fto come by."
OL,16,FOne of the first investigations
OL,17,Fcarried out by a new body tasked with
OL,18,Fprobing outstanding cases from the
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland Troubles will be into
OL,20,FGuildford attack.
