OL,7,FThe Independent Commission for
OL,8,FReconciliation and Information
OL,9,FRecovery (ICRIR) will examine the
OL,10,Fatrocity at the Horse and Groom and a
OL,11,Fbomb that detonated 30 minutes later
OL,12,Fat the Seven Stars pub in the city.
OL,14,FThe Guildford Four and Maguire Seven
OL,15,Fwere wrongly convicted of the attacks
OL,16,Fin one of the UK's biggest
OL,17,Fmiscarriages of justice.
OL,19,FAn IRA terror cell later claimed
OL,20,Fresponsibility.
